{"word":"Maachah","slug":"maachah","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>Maachah</b> <a href=\"#/H4601\">H4601</a> <br/> 1. Son of Nahor<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=22&verse=24'>Gen 22:24</a><br/> 2. Called Maacah, mother of Absalom<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=10&chapter=3&verse=3'>2Sa 3:3</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=13&chapter=3&verse=2'>1Ch 3:2</a><br/> 3. Called Maoch, father of Achish<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=9&chapter=27&verse=2'>1Sa 27:2</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=11&chapter=2&verse=39'>1Ki 2:39</a><br/> 4. Called Michaiah, mother of Abijam and grandmother of Asa<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=11&chapter=15&verse=2'>1Ki 15:2</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=11&chapter=15&verse=13'>1Ki 15:13</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=14&chapter=11&verse=23'>2Ch 11:23</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=14&chapter=13&verse=2'>2Ch 13:2</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=14&chapter=15&verse=16'>2Ch 15:16</a><br/> 5. Wife of Machir<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=13&chapter=7&verse=16'>1Ch 7:16</a><br/> 6. Concubine of Caleb<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=13&chapter=2&verse=48'>1Ch 2:48</a><br/> 7. Wife of Jehiel<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=13&chapter=8&verse=29'>1Ch 8:29</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=13&chapter=9&verse=35'>1Ch 9:35</a><br/> 8. Father of Hanan<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=13&chapter=11&verse=43'>1Ch 11:43</a><br/> 9. Father of Shephatiah<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=13&chapter=27&verse=16'>1Ch 27:16</a><br/> 10. Called Maacah and Maachathi, a small kingdom east of Bashan<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=5&chapter=3&verse=14'>Deu 3:14</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=6&chapter=12&verse=5'>Jos 12:5</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=10&chapter=10&verse=6'>2Sa 10:6</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=10&chapter=10&verse=8'>2Sa 10:8</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=13&chapter=19&verse=7'>1Ch 19:7</a>"}]}